-shaped-the-cold-war%2Farticleshow%2F130590178.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Quixote%20Studios%20Lays%20Off%2070%2C%20Winds%20Down%20L.A.%20Locations%20Amid%20Production%20Slump%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22Quixote%20Studios%20is%20shuttering%20its%20Atlanta-based%20production%20services%20business%20and%20winding%20down%20its%20soundstage%20business%20in%20L.A.%20amid%20an%20ongoing%20production%20slump%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20Tuesday.%20The%20changes%20will%20mean%20layoffs%20for%20about%2070%20people%20in%20Atlanta%20and%20Los%20Angeles.%20Hudson%20Pacific%20Properties%20bought%20the%20company%20in%202022%20for%20%24360%20million%2C%20but%20has%20since%20had%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777410096000%2C%22image%22%3A%22%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236732572%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bizarre%20tax%20laws%20in%20US%20could%20drain%2030%2B%20nations%E2%80%99%20World%20Cup%20earnings%20as%20FIFA%20fails%20to%20secure%20exemption%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F130589917.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%202026%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20faces%20an%20unexpected%20financial%20divide%20as%20US%20tax%20laws%20and%20uneven%20international%20treaties%20mean%20teams%20will%20be%20taxed%20differently%20on%20tournament%20earnings.%20While%20FIFA%20holds%20tax-exempt%20status%2C%20many%20federations%20do%20not%2C%20leaving%20non-European%20nations%20particularly%20exposed.%20With%20varying%20state%20taxes%20and%20limited%20exemptions%2C%20the%20expanded%2048-team%20format%20risks%20creating%20major%20economic%20disparities%20between%20participants.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777408413000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130590071%2Cimgsize-110936.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Finternational-sports%2Fbizarre-tax-laws-in-us-could-